03:40.136 --> 03:42.135
[Stacey] Are you coming, too?

03:42.136 --> 03:44.052
Uh, no. It's the first I've heard of it.

03:44.053 --> 03:45.614
So you'll come.

03:45.615 --> 03:48.053
I can't. I've got to grade some papers.

03:48.054 --> 03:50.552
Dad, it's Halloween. You have to come.

03:50.553 --> 03:52.558
[Trevor] No, Dad probably
didn't make the guest list.

03:52.559 --> 03:54.575
Why not? He wrote Sasha's movie.

03:54.576 --> 03:56.886
Nobody cares about the writer, stupid.

03:56.887 --> 03:59.302
Dad's, like, the most
disposable person on set.

03:59.303 --> 04:00.809
Trevor, don't call your sister stupid.

04:00.810 --> 04:02.642
I'm not going if Dad's not invited.

04:02.643 --> 04:04.469
Oh, come on now, that's silly.

04:04.470 --> 04:06.344
- You'll enjoy it.
- But I want to do something

04:06.345 --> 04:08.469
together, as a family.

04:08.470 --> 04:11.155
[Trevor] You remember that
Halloween in Brooklyn,

04:11.156 --> 04:13.010
when Mom took home the
wrong mummy from the party

04:13.011 --> 04:14.177
- and left Martin?
- [laughs]

04:14.178 --> 04:15.719
Because she couldn't tell the difference

04:15.720 --> 04:17.094
between him and the other kid.

04:17.095 --> 04:19.531
[laughs] You remember that?

04:19.531 --> 04:21.010
Yeah. And then, in the end,

04:21.011 --> 04:22.469
the other kid didn't want to go home,

04:22.470 --> 04:24.023
because being with the Solloways,

04:24.024 --> 04:25.825
even as an imposter,

04:25.826 --> 04:27.636
was more fun than being
with his own family.

04:27.637 --> 04:28.803
- [Noah laughs]
- I remember, too.

04:28.804 --> 04:30.260
[Trevor] N-No, you don't.

04:30.261 --> 04:31.719
You've just heard the stories.

04:31.720 --> 04:33.146
You were a baby.

04:33.886 --> 04:37.469
[dishes clinking]

04:37.470 --> 04:40.217
Why don't we all go out
for dinner this week?

04:40.218 --> 04:42.451
I'll see if I can get it
on your mother's calendar.

04:43.990 --> 04:45.156
[Helen] Okay.

04:47.470 --> 04:51.273
[echoing] Well, yeah, tell her
I said, uh, I know that it's

04:51.274 --> 04:52.678
