expensive, but why spend

04:52.679 --> 04:53.928
all the money on the chaise if you

04:53.929 --> 04:56.052
don't want to cover it
with an amazing fabric?

04:56.053 --> 04:57.613
[wistful music]

04:57.614 --> 04:59.031
