05:05.095 --> 05:06.469
Mm. Her assistant.

05:06.470 --> 05:08.574
- She has an assistant?
- [Helen] Okay, great.

05:08.575 --> 05:10.407
Thank you for doing this.

05:10.408 --> 05:11.634
Happy to help.

05:11.635 --> 05:14.594
Trevor said he'd quit school if
I let my mother drop him off.

05:14.595 --> 05:17.344
We were just remembering
that Halloween when you, uh,

05:17.345 --> 05:19.631
picked up the wrong mummy and
left Martin at the party.

05:19.632 --> 05:21.844
- [chuckles] Remember that?
- I never did that.

05:21.845 --> 05:23.177
- Yeah, you did.
- Yeah, you did, Mom.

05:23.178 --> 05:25.260
- Yeah, you did.
- Wow.

05:25.261 --> 05:27.219
You guys were practically
raised by wolves,

05:27.220 --> 05:28.606
and yet, you turned out so well.

05:28.607 --> 05:30.552
Can you get your shit for school?

05:30.553 --> 05:32.303
- Yeah, okay.
- [sighs]

05:34.842 --> 05:36.759
[Margaret sighs]

05:39.679 --> 05:40.882
Well... [chuckles]

05:41.422 --> 05:43.481
I guess I'll take the trash out,

05:43.482 --> 05:45.844
since no one else is doing it.

05:45.845 --> 05:47.334
Thanks, Mom.

05:50.186 --> 05:51.602
How are you?

05:51.603 --> 05:54.552
- Good. You?
- Good.

05:54.553 --> 05:55.791
Been a while.

05:55.792 --> 05:57.856
Yeah. Yeah, I wanted to, um...

05:58.896 --> 06:01.386
I wanted to talk to you
about what happened.

06:01.387 --> 06:03.177
What do you mean?

06:03.178 --> 06:05.256
You know, in the karaoke bar.

06:06.706 --> 06:08.080
How much do you remember?

06:08.081 --> 06:09.561
Enough.

06:10.804 --> 06:12.719
I think, um...

06:12.720 --> 06:14.386
I think watching this
movie getting made,

06:14.387 --> 06:15.928
it's-it's bringing up a lot of stuff,

06:15.929 --> 06:17.763
and I'm-I'm not handling it properly.

06:17.764 --> 06:19.436
Mm-hmm.

06:21.303 --> 06:24.260
So my feelings over the, you
know, ownership of the book

06:24.261 --> 06:25.928
and trying to get the story right,

06:25.929 --> 06:28.260
I, uh, maybe I...

06:28.261 --> 06:29.386
Maybe that spilled over to you,

06:29.387 --> 06:31.103
and I blurred the lines a little.

06:31.104 --> 06:32.428
You think?

06:33.387 --> 06:35.594
Anyway, the point is, I'm-I'm sorry.

06:35.595 --> 06:37.230
I shouldn't have...

06:38.762 --> 06:40.511
I'm sorry, you know.

06:40.512 --> 06:42.656
You can do what you want
with your personal life.

06:42.657 --> 06:44.671
I should just give you some privacy.

06:45.886 --> 06:47.552
All I want is to maintain a healthy

06:47.553 --> 06:50.220
co-parenting relationship,
for the sake of the kids.

06:57.378 --> 06:59.461
