09:48.345 --> 09:50.260
- Walking the walk.
- [Noah laughs]

09:50.261 --> 09:51.969
Yeah, so sorry I called the meeting

09:51.970 --> 09:55.427
and, uh, raised a red
flag; it's just that, um,

09:55.428 --> 09:59.992
there's been a, uh, uh,
a miscommunication,

09:59.993 --> 10:02.283
and, um, I've been banned from the set.

10:02.284 --> 10:04.135
So I need you to help me

10:04.136 --> 10:06.956
smooth it over or whatever and...
so I can go back to work.

10:07.929 --> 10:10.135
When you say you've been
banned from set, what...

10:10.136 --> 10:12.556
- what does that mean exactly?
- Banned by who?

10:12.557 --> 10:14.309
By, uh, Sasha.

10:14.310 --> 10:15.995
Mann?

10:15.996 --> 10:17.260
Yeah, Sasha Mann.

10:17.261 --> 10:18.804
[both] Huh.

10:21.958 --> 10:25.343
Listen, we love that you
want to see the process

10:25.344 --> 10:27.042
- all the way through...
- It shows passion.

10:27.043 --> 10:29.902
...but really, is there anything
more boring than production?

10:29.903 --> 10:31.094
Yawn city.

10:31.095 --> 10:33.594
No, guys, no. Look...

10:34.388 --> 10:35.969
this has been a ten-year journey

10:35.970 --> 10:37.969
trying to realize this book as a movie,

10:37.970 --> 10:40.744
and... it's my life story,

10:40.745 --> 10:42.924
so I-I need to be there

10:42.925 --> 10:44.578
- to make sure it's done right.
- We get it, Noah.

10:44.579 --> 10:46.678
This is your baby, but
let's not lose sight

10:46.679 --> 10:48.135
of the big picture.

10:48.136 --> 10:51.427
When the town sees "written by
Sasha Mann and Noah Solloway"

10:51.428 --> 10:53.260
on a box office smash,

10:53.261 --> 10:55.511
every above-the-title star
in Hollywood is gonna be

10:55.512 --> 10:57.719
knocking down your door to
cowrite their passion project.

10:57.720 --> 10:59.427
