12:59.002 --> 13:01.135
Did you just... did
you just talk to her?

13:01.136 --> 13:02.678
I'm afraid I have another call.

13:02.679 --> 13:03.969
I'll give Ms. Butler your message.

13:03.970 --> 13:06.109
- No, I don't want to leave a message...
- [line beeps]

13:07.929 --> 13:09.637
[mutters quietly]

13:10.679 --> 13:12.680
This is tulle, Dad.

13:12.681 --> 13:14.260
I said lace.

13:14.261 --> 13:15.886
Well, what do you want me to do, Trevor?

13:15.887 --> 13:17.386
- Take it back?
- You know what? No.

13:17.387 --> 13:19.135
There's no time.

13:19.136 --> 13:21.260
Guess I'm just gonna have
to wear this boring,

13:21.261 --> 13:23.594
plain garter belt.

13:23.595 --> 13:25.588
Trevor, I think you look fantastic.

13:25.589 --> 13:27.042
Yeah, thanks, Dad.

13:27.043 --> 13:29.054
When is Mom taking you to this party?

13:29.055 --> 13:30.618
- It's almost six.
- [Margaret] Noah?

13:31.127 --> 13:33.067
May I talk to you for a minute?

13:33.834 --> 13:35.260
There's been a change of plans

13:35.261 --> 13:37.323
which shouldn't be a surprise to anyone.

13:37.324 --> 13:38.668
Why? What's going on?

13:38.669 --> 13:40.168
Helen's working late.

13:40.169 --> 13:42.427
She's asked me to drive
them to Sasha Mann's.

